Package smarthome.domain.sensormodel.vo

Class SensorModelName

java.lang.Object
smarthome.domain.sensormodel.vo.SensorModelName
All Implemented Interfaces:
DomainId, ValueObject
public class SensorModelName extends Object implements DomainId
The SensorModelName class represents the model name of a sensor in the smart home domain. It implements the DomainId interface, indicating that its equality is based on its value rather than identity. It contains a single field: sensorModelName, represented as a String. The class provides a getter method for this field and an overridden sameAs method for equality check.
